desc_long							评测						“Metamorphabet is sweetness itself, but it is also gorgeously disturbing.”Eurogamer“The experience comes to life in robust, surprising animations full of elasticity, inventiveness and charm and is just trippy enough to make adult players feel astounded by the transmogrifications that happen with each tap.”Kotaku“Metamorphabet is a thing of joy, on the surface simple, underneath a labour of love. And you’ll love it too.”Rock, Paper, Shotgun												关于这款游戏							Metamorphabet is a playful, interactive alphabet for all ages. Poke, prod, drag, and spin the letters of the alphabet to reveal surprising and luminous transformations.						
